# App Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000
NODE_ENV=development

# MiniPay Development Mode
# In development (NODE_ENV=development), any Ethereum wallet (MetaMask, etc.)
# will be treated as MiniPay for local testing. This allows you to test the
# full worker flow without needing a real Android device with MiniPay.
#
# For production testing with real MiniPay:
# 1. Install ngrok: npm install -g ngrok
# 2. Start dev server: npm run dev
# 3. Start ngrok tunnel: ngrok http 3000
# 4. Open ngrok URL in MiniPay app on Android device
# 5. Test full flow: onboard → task → withdraw
#
# Production (NODE_ENV=production) always enforces MiniPay-only detection.
